    "en": {
      "title": "Dhamma Polonnaru to the West",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Former President Maithripala Sirisena's son Mr. Dham Sirisena has been appointed as the new Sri Lankan Nationalist Party organizer for the Polonnaruwa West Constituency.",
        "Appointment of Mr. Dhamma Sirisena, who served as the Chairman of the Polonnaruwa District Youth Committee of the Sri Lanka Freedom Party, Mr. Maithripala Sirisena, the Chairman of the party, presented Mr. Dhamma Sirisena with the appointment letter for that position.",
        "Sri Lanka Freedom Party General Secretary Mr. Dayasiri Jayasekara participated in this event."
      ],
